  "texts": [
    "Using the invariant mass and transverse momentum of the jet calculated using all constituents and not just the leading 30 constituents was also studied.",
    "A negligible impact on performance was observed when comparing these options.",
    "The values calculated using only the leading 30 constituents were chosen in order to test for the diagonality of the generated jet momenta and invariant masses.",
    "Whether to use the transverse momentum or relative transverse momentum of the constituents was also studied in conjunction with log(p T) and log(p T + 1) transformations.",
    "Using log(p T + 1) for the constituent momenta was found to perform best in most metrics, and resulted in better agreement for low p T constituents."
  ],
